    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3522764/" class="title-link">比前三本更大胆</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3522764"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3925163/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3925163-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3925163/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">安康</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-08-09"
      class="main-meta">2010-08-09 09:12:02</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3522764_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  这本书出来之前，据说袁老师已经喝茶了，所以一直担心《历史4》能不能出版。没想到出来之后，比前三本更胆大。《历史2》只写到49年，而《历史4》写到了80年代末，再加上评论的是别国，所以可以无所顾忌地评论当代史的许多事件，而不像《历史2》有那么多禁区。既然用不着遮遮掩...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/3522764/#comments">(5回应)</a>
